data.title: When did Elena Konanykhin die?
data.meta_description:
I believe that she died in 2008 There are news videos of her in
2004 here http://66.39.99.53/media.htm and in the Authors note at
the end of Brian Haigs book The Hunted he stated that she died 2
weeks before he finished his books on the Konanykhin's that book
was published in 2009. [by Scott Snow]
======================
My name is Alex Konanykhin; I just encountered this page.. Elena
was my wife. She died on March 30, 2007, two months after first
cancer symptom.
